              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text ibS2ktz15fCisBTjP"><h3>Can I answer and make calls?</h3></div
              ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="iLceCvhzsXwVNP1ZK">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="instant-icon">
