                ><p><strong>Yes. </strong>The Carbinox Edge includes a built-in speaker and microphone, allowing you to <strong>make and receive calls straight from your wrist </strong>when connected to your smartphone via Bluetooth. Perfect for hands-free communication on the job or on the move.</p><p></p></div></div></div
