              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text i7hcGApA6hJNQhTFP"
                ><p>The Carbinox Edge features <strong>dual-band GNSS</strong>, allowing it to provide <strong>standalone GPS tracking </strong>without requiring a phone connection. This is especially useful for outdoor activities where phone signal may be weak or unavailable.</p></div
              ></div
            ></div
