              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iCaK6RDAPjTzDcRC6"
                ><p>Yes — the Edge is rated <strong>5ATM and IP69K waterproof</strong>, plus it’s <strong>dustproof, shockproof</strong>, and built to take on mud, oil, water, and extreme conditions. You can wear it confidently while swimming, on job sites, or in the rain.</p><p></p></div></div></div
