              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text iGdCDMUYcBdnHakJc"><h3>Is my smartphone compatible with the Carbinox watches?</h3></div
              ><div data-instant-type="icon" class="iCuOpsF2orDnIIVta">
